title: Looking for some people to queue up with
body:
hello! I've recently joined on league and currently have no one to queue up with and I'd prefer to queue up with a group instead, as I've noticed it practically takes forever to queue when solo queuing....
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

Originally I had been playing on one of my friends accounts before deciding to make my own. 
so Here I am
incase you couldn't tell my IGN is baboju

I'm currently level seven.

so feel free to add me
